values.name: REPACKAGING_FROM_DRUMS_SOLID_SLUDGE_OPEN_TOP
values.id: Repackaging from Drums (Solid / Sludge) - Open Top

restQueries.name: GetAgentInfo
restQueries.jpql: select o from pbksb_Agent o where o.agent_ID = :agent_ID

restQueries.name: GetUserInfo
restQueries.jpql: select o from pbksb_CustomerUser o where o.fullname = :fullname

restQueries.name: GetMHEJobDetailsByJobTicket
restQueries.jpql: select e from pbksb_Job_MHE e where e.job_ticket = :jobticket order by e.id desc

restQueries.name: GetMHEJobTicketByCustomerCode
restQueries.jpql: select o from pbksb_Job_MHE o where o.job.requestform.customeruser.customer.code = :customercode order by o.id desc

restQueries.name: PSB_ListRequestForm
restQueries.jpql: select o from pbksb_Job_PSB o join o.agent c where c.agent_ID = :agent_ID

restQueries.name: MHE_ListRequestForm
restQueries.jpql: select o from pbksb_Requestform o where o.customer.code = :code AND o.status <> 'ENDORSED'

restQueries.name: UpdateVessel
restQueries.jpql: select o from pbksb_Vessel o where o.name = :name
